{"tid":206074,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"百麗國際(1880) 停牌","createTime":"2017-04-18T07:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T03:19:38.000Z","uid":46197,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2333ba37ffa181d7fb1b57c780395293f4bf9312","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"百麗國際(01880)今早停牌，外電引述知情人士透露，鼎輝投資正與百麗國際的管理層一起研究潛在的收購交易。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，相關公告最早或於本周公布。<br />\n<br />\n百麗國際、鼎暉投資的代表未立即對此作出置評。<br />\n<br />\n百麗國際停牌，待根據香港公司收購及合併守則，發出一份性質屬股價敏感公告，停牌前報5.27元。"},{"pid":"735e5350003d5405406acea3ed4ca46e31b17a01","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"升定跌？"},{"pid":"5dbf4398d477b5f5fdc2e490f0a2b13cfd3e8b89","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"有無古惑"},{"pid":"de299cb19d2b683c5e24347efc3dd7446edfc5be","tid":206074,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"揸緊百麗的人有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5145ddd457bb38de88d8fd60df2b16ecea0235","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸緊百麗的人有福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17407a5b6f37231bf77a1da4f3fbc02ea409632c","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"有無人有消息？<br />\n停左兩星期"},{"pid":"3d1efb8c01c5ef7c2ccb83d298c6ca8f1aeeb777","tid":206074,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人有消息？<br />\n停左兩星期</blockquote><br />\n咪基金收購囉<br />\n你坐左好多咩?"},{"pid":"a31567174b5f937bd89401032965f9e1993af376","tid":206074,"uid":46197,"like":0,"dislike":0